'''Alessandrina "Sandra" Mondaini''' ( Italian: [ˈSandra mondaˈiːni] ; 1 Nzeri 1931 &#x2013; 21 Nzeri 2010) yari umukinnyi wa filime w' umutaliyani akaba kandi yarayoboraga ibiganiro kuri  televiziyo . Yagaragaye muri filime 30 hagati ya 1953 na 2008.

Yavukiye i Milan mu [[Ubutaliyani|Butaliyani]], ashakana n'umukinnyi wa filime Raimondo Vianello mu 1962. Afatanije n' umugabo we, yakiriye ibiganiro bitandukanye kuri tereviziyo y' Ubutaliyani harimo: ''Tante scuse'', ''Di nuovo tante scuse'', ''Attenti a noi due'', ''Sandra e Raimondo Show'' na ''Stasera niente di nuovo'' . Hagati ya 1988 na 2007 yagize uruhare runini muri sitcom, Casa Vaniello izwi cyane yo mu Butaliyani. Ibikorwa bye bya nyuma yari filime ya''Crociera Vianello'' yakuwe muri ''Casa Vianello'' .

Yapfuye ku ya 21 Nzeri 2010 i Milan afite imyaka 79, amezi atanu nyuma y'uko umugabo we apfuye.  <ref>[http://www.italymagazine.com/italy/milano/italy-says-farewell-sandra Italy says farewell to Sandra]</ref>

